.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, prince, ritmeester, pall-mall
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the police-officer##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Cigar         | vegafina | prince   | pall-mall   | ritmeester         |

