.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the fan of folk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the fan of jazz##2
2. the freelancer is between the fan of folk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | 7up      | iced-tea   | milk   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

