The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the craftsman house is the fisherman##1
 2. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the fisherman is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the tower house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the fan of metal is the wooden house##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| House          | farmhouse        | tower    | wooden | craftsman   |
