 5. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsrose##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
